324
00:47:40.480 --> 00:47:41.581
Da li bi volela to?

325
00:47:43.617 --> 00:47:44.702
Da?

326
00:47:45.819 --> 00:47:46.937
Sačuvaj tu misao.

327
00:47:56.897 --> 00:47:59.599
