Molim te.

555
01:16:06.453 --> 01:16:07.521
Arija!

556
01:16:18.866 --> 01:16:20.100
Izađi napolje!

557
01:16:22.069 --> 01:16:24.471
Izađi napolje i spusti pušku dole!

558
01:16:26.273 --> 01:16:28.175
Znam da si tamo, mister!

559
01:16:29.009 --> 01:16:30.077
Spusti je dole samo!

560
01:16:32.613 --> 01:16:35.282
