01:19:49.143 --> 01:19:50.444
Idemo. Hajde.

627
01:19:52.779 --> 01:19:53.847
Idi.

628
01:19:57.784 --> 01:19:58.919
Prekinite to.

629
01:22:43.850 --> 01:22:44.884
