630
01:22:45.919 --> 01:22:46.954
Baci pištolj!

631
01:22:47.854 --> 01:22:49.223
Uradi to!

632
01:22:49.257 --> 01:22:50.390
Ubiću je!

633
01:22:51.591 --> 01:22:53.793
Uradi šta ti kažem, mister!

634
01:22:53.827 --> 01:22:54.894
Uradi to!

635
